# Agent continuity (on demand)

**Core:** [`ppe-operator-core.mdc`](ppe-operator-core.mdc)

Load for Google Docs roles, context-window closeout, asset discovery, or extended steering reads. See [`AGENT_CONTINUITY_BRIEF.md`](docs/SOP/AGENT_CONTINUITY_BRIEF.md), [`CONTEXT_RULES.md`](docs/CONTEXT_RULES.md).

**Asset auto-discovery (mandatory):** When the operator asks to **add, enable, or hook up any asset**, run **`python scripts/discover_asset_data_source.py --asset <ID> --json` first** (same turn, before replying) and **execute `next_action`** — see [`asset-auto-discovery.mdc`](asset-auto-discovery.mdc) and [`ASSET_DATA_SOURCE_DISCOVERY_V1.md`](../../docs/SOP/ASSET_DATA_SOURCE_DISCOVERY_V1.md). **Never ask** which exchange; scan Deribit → Bybit (crypto) or yfinance (equity) automatically.

**Asset probe (verify only):** After registry changes, run `python scripts/probe_asset_data_source.py --asset <ID> --json`.

**Google Docs:** never write PPE Master via MCP; MSOS Repo Truth via sync scripts only.

## Operator fix notifications (phone)

When fixing blocked operator state (`ERROR`, `IDE_BUILD`, `FIX_PLAN`, `STALE_STATE`):

1. **Start:** `python scripts/ppe_notify_fix.py --working --issue "<verdict>: <blocker>"`
2. **Finish:** `python scripts/ppe_notify_fix.py --resolved --issue "<same label>" --summary "..."`

